## Videos [/api/v1/videos{?category,limit,offset}]

Resources related to video content.

+ Parameters
    + category (optional, enum[string]) - The video content category.
        + Default: general
        + Members            
            + business
            + entertainment
            + general
            + health
            + science
            + sports
            + technology
    + limit (optional, number) - The number of results to return.
        + Default: 20
    + offset (optional, number) - The (zero-based) offset of the first item in the collection to return.
        + Default: 0

### Get Videos [GET]

This action allows you to query videos.

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (object)
        + videos (required, array[Video]) - The list of videos.
        + total_count (optional, number) - The total number of available videos.

    + Body
        
